<h3 class="mag_top_none bold">SMS Services</h3>
<p class="p">Textedly is the World’s Best Text Messaging Company for two reasons. Our online SMS Mass Texting Messaging service is beautifully easy to use and simple to afford. Our plans start as low as $20 per month.</p>
<p>When your customers or contacts Text your own personal Textedly Keyword to the short code 33222, our platform will automatically add them to your contact list and instantly Text back a fully customizable response. The benefits that Text Messaging has over traditional forms of communicating are Texts become a personal way of communication. And because Text Messaging has a 10x better open rate then emails, you are sure to get a rapid response on your efforts. Textedly’s easy to follow online guide walks you through how to use the platform. Our bulk SMS Text Messaging services works for you, enabling you to instantly reach thousands of&nbsp;contacts and engage with them, promote your services, or make announcements. We make SMS Messaging fun!</p>
